Infrastructure Products for Worldwide Markets
 L.B. Foster supplies transportation, construction, utility, energy, recreation and agriculture markets with the materials necessary to build and maintain their infrastructure. Today, L.B. Foster Company is a leading manufacturer, fabricator and distributor of quality transportation and construction materials. The company is committed to meeting customer requirements and increasing buyer satisfaction. 


We Solve the Challenges that Matter Most
 Our innovative technology is fueling new product development that defines L.B. Foster as the solutions leader in energy, construction and transportation markets. The L.B Foster team is delivering the products and solutions necessary to satisfy our customer's most demanding challenges. Our company is expanding and adapting to changing customer needs with industry-leading products and services.


Our Products have Built a Legacy of Landmarks
 Today's infrastructure is built on L.B. Foster's legacy. For more than a century, our company has provided the materials necessary to construct and maintain major transportation, construction and utility projects. L.B. Foster products have recently contributed to the improvement of many landmark structures including the Panama Canal, Brooklyn Bridge and New Orleans Flood Walls.




Learn more about our rich history and legacy of quality products and landmark projects. 











L.B. Foster Ball Winch Facility  Completes Technip  Trinidad & Tobago Project
L.B.  Foster Ball Winch completes application of protective FBE for  North American unit of Technip, a  Paris-based oilfield services firm, for new BP Juniper Offshore Gas facility in  Trinidad and Tobago.


Bay Area SMART Train to  Begin Operation Soon on CXT Concrete Ties
Northern  California's new transit rail system  is almost ready to begin operation on CXT concrete rail ties between Sonoma  County Airport and San Rafael in Marin County.


Our Innovative Technology Monitors Critical Rail Safety Concerns
Damaged rail and defective wheels are critical concerns  for rail operators worldwide. L.B. Foster's  Wheel Impact Load Detector (WILD) monitors rail wheel impairment and our RailStress Monitorâ˘ provides rail break alerts and real-time  buckle warnings.


We're Designing Advanced Rail Products and  Systems
L.B. Foster's TEW group of companies specializes in rail engineering for control room,  passenger information, security  and trackside signaling applications. The UK-based team is designing advanced rail products  and systems that offer new solutions for challenging  problems.


L.B. Foster Supplies Piling for Iowa Dam Hydro Electric Project
L.B.  Foster Piling provided PZCâ˘ 26 steel  sheet piling and wide flange king pile beams for the retrofit of the Des Moines  River's Red Rock Dam into a hydro electric power generation plant.




